  <li id="comment-23650" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01493708300940204826" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=586#comment-23650"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-06-17T02:18:37-04:00">Friday, June 17, 2011 at 2:18 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Vicki, I like your plastic bag idea!</p>
<p>Nancy, I&#39;ll bet that would be delicious.  Can&#39;t imagine that it wouldn&#39;t be!  I do like what the dollop on top does, though.  It&#39;s nice to be able to taste the aioli separate from the yolk mixture, and the aioli makes the whole mouthful very creamy, which is nice, too.</p>
