    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh Molly, I hope you feel better soon&#8230;..The deviled eggs should help.<br />So enamored of the little buggers are we in our home that Susan, who works at Random House, will often go downstairs to the cafeteria for lunch, buy 2 hardboiled eggs, and bring them back upstairs with tiny cafeteria packets of Hellman&#39;s mayo, mustard, and hot sauce. Right there, in her office, surrounded by stacks of manuscripts, she takes out her little bowl, mixes the yolks together with with the mustard and mayo and hot sauce, pops everything back into the egg whites, and voila, she has herself some deviled eggs.<br />Mighty powerful stuff.</p>
    </div>

