    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Wow, deviled eggs, this brings back memories. I never have developed a taste for them, but everyone in my family just adores them.  My Dad makes them on special occasions, and I think he sprinkles paprika &#8212; or something paprika-colored anyway &#8212; on them. They get devoured instantly, which I just do not understand.  </p>
<p>I always thought of them as a Southern staple, and having grown up with them at all the family functions, I never really considered that they could be elegant! </p>
<p>I should pass this recipe on to my Dad and see what he thinks. : )</p>
