    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Jen/YVR</cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=586#comment-23696"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-06-18T21:08:43-04:00">Saturday, June 18, 2011 at 9:08 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just last weekend I made devilled eggs for an afternoon tea-themed baby shower. I did them with the flavours you would see in bernaise sauce &#8211; white wine vinegar and finely diced shallots reduced down, fresh tarragon, and lemon zest, all mashed into the yolks. Turned out very nicely &#8211; I would definitely make them again. </p>
<p>Side note &#8211; there&#39;s a restaurant here that does a beautiful beef carpaccio topped with fried capers. Love &#39;em!</p>
    </div>

